OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781104294
OL,3,CMan jailed for high speed crash that
OL,4,Cinjured four people
OL,6,FA Kent man has been jailed for nearly
OL,7,Ffour years for dangerous driving and
OL,8,Ffleeing the scene of a crash which
OL,9,Finjured four people.
OL,11,FLuke Wells, 31, of Lawping Close,
OL,12,FMinster, was driving a red Vauxhall
OL,13,FAstra at high speed when he collided
OL,14,Fwith another vehicle in July 2024.
OL,16,FAll four occupants of a grey Peugeot
OL,17,Fwere injured in the incident, which
OL,18,Fhappened on Queensborough Road.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
