PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781104294
OL,3,CMan jailed for high speed crash that
OL,4,Cinjured four people
OL,6,FThe front seat passenger of the car
OL,7,Fsuffered serious, life threatening
OL,8,Finjuries, including multiple fractures.
OL,10,FThe driver and another passenger also
OL,11,Ffractured bones.
OL,13,FWitnesses told Kent Police they had
OL,14,Fseen the driver of the Astra flee on
OL,15,Ffoot, discarding his sandals in a
OL,16,Fdriveway.
OL,18,FThe driver was later identified as
OL,19,FWells, who was found by officers at
OL,20,Fhis home address.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781104294
OL,3,CMan jailed for high speed crash that
OL,4,Cinjured four people
OL,6,FHe initially denied any involvement,
OL,7,Fclaiming that he had sold the Astra a
OL,8,Ffew days before the collision.
OL,10,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FWells was later charged with three
OL,16,Fcounts of causing serious injury by
OL,17,Fdangerous driving and attempting to
OL,18,Fpervert the course of justice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
