OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781104294
OL,3,CMan jailed for high speed crash that
OL,4,Cinjured four people
OL,6,FIt came after officers had collected
OL,7,Fseveral key pieces of evidence linking
OL,8,Fhim to the crash, including forensic
OL,9,Fmaterial from the scene that matched
OL,10,Fthat of Wells.
OL,12,FOfficers also found evidence at his
OL,13,Fhome address that Wells had attempted
OL,14,Fto change his appearance by shaving
OL,15,Foff some of his hair and beard.
OL,17,FWells eventually pleaded guilty to all
OL,18,Fof the charges at Maidstone Crown
OL,19,FCourt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
