OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1781104294
OL,3,CMan jailed for high speed crash that
OL,4,Cinjured four people
OL,6,FHe was sentenced earlier this month to
OL,7,Fthree years and 10 months in jail, and
OL,8,Fdisqualified from driving for four
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FInvestigating officer Police Constable
OL,12,FSean Browne said: "Wells has shown
OL,13,Fhimself to have no regard for the
OL,14,Fwelfare of others, thinking only of
OL,15,Fhimself when he decided to leave the
OL,16,Fscene of the collision.
OL,18,F"He knew exactly what he had done, and
OL,19,Fby trying to change his appearance,
OL,20,Falso showed a total disregard for the
OL,21,Flaw.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
